TORQ – 2018 Cherry Kickoff Party

Life is more than just black and white, so get ready to #DanceInColor; TORQ returns this March, but it’s time to take it to the next level! EPC Productions has partnered with LaFantasy Productions to bring you NYC’s official Cherry Kick-Off Party for Cherry 2018: Kaleidoscope. Returning home to RetroClub NYC, the event will be held on Sunday, March 25th at a NEW time of 7PM-1AM. TORQ will be powered by the sounds of DJ Serving Ovahness, so get ready for an electrifying Sunday!
